{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"1437","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":null,"news_on_top":"1","news_title":"極端氣候因素 影響亞洲股市與經濟","news_summary":null,"image_path":null,"news_des":"","news_content":"<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>2023-04-26 16:06 台灣醒報／記者莊瑞萌╱台北報導</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E6%B0%A3%E5%80%99.png' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; width: 100%;' /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>亞洲溫度持續上升，對於性命與財產都將帶來損失。(Photo by Rexness on Flickr used under Creative Commons license)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr style='box-sizing: content-box; border-radius: 0px; height: 1px; margin: 20px 0px; border-top-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), transparent); color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;' />\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>極端氣候打亂食物供應，股市也跟著受害。金融分析公司指出，受到氣候變遷加劇天災規模更激烈以及不穩定後，造成供需預測也更難精準掌握。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-weight: 700;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>暴雨讓工廠停擺</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>據《The Edge Markets》報導，澳洲礦業公司紐克雷斯特本月因為氣旋襲擊西澳海岸，造成黃金礦坑關閉導致該公司股價大跌，暴雨與洪水更迫使其他礦業公司煤礦生產也受阻。至於今年2月印度出現世紀罕見高溫，隨後並傳出牛隻死亡數量激增，使當地產乳量罕見下滑，隨著未來仍會出現高溫及夏季需求增加，讓當地帕拉格牛奶食品等業者股價也跟著上漲。</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>金英證券分析師吉格爾沙阿表示，「由於氣候多變，讓預測需求和產出趨勢並進行行業或股票預測變得複雜，如果這種情況不受控制，農業和食物鏈將面臨重大威脅。」</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-weight: 700;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>亞洲高溫仍持續</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>近來預期聖嬰現象可能會造成亞洲與澳洲未來迎接更熱的天氣，泰國農業公司與飲料商公司的股價也頓時成為寵兒。彭博資訊分析師錢杜卡指出，「今年可能的聖嬰現象恐會導致季風降雨不足而阻礙農作物生產。」</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>據《艾菲通訊社》報導，今年4月是泰國最熱、最乾燥的月份，由於氣溫已飆升至危險程度，政府當局緊急呼籲兒童、老人和病人等族群小心，防止出現健康併發症。除了氣候變遷的影響外，預計未來幾個月東南亞還將受到聖嬰現象影響，導致降雨減少和溫度升高。</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-weight: 700;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>政府率先因應</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>菲律賓總統小馬可仕表示，他已下令各部門和政府機構設法降低聖嬰現象的影響，避免農作物因缺水而受損。去年10月，聯合國和紅十字會在報告中指出，由於氣候變遷，未來熱浪將更加頻繁、激烈和致命。</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'>【更多精采內容，詳見</span><a href='https://anntw.com/' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 158, 184); text-decoration-line: none; outline: 0px !important;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>臺灣醒報</span></a><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'>】</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'>資料來源:&nbsp;</span><a href='https://udn.com/news/story/6809/7124594' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 158, 184); text-decoration-line: none; outline: 0px !important;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>https://udn.com/news/story/6809/7124594</span></a></span></p>\r\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2023-04-28","clk_count":"27"}},"__N_SSG":true}